{
  "texts": [
    "This lipophilicity dataset is curated from the ChEMBL database, providing experimental results of octanol/water partition coefficients (logD at pH 7.4) for 4200 compounds.",
    "FreeSolvDataset: The FreeSolv dataset consists of experimental and computationally derived solvation free energies of small molecules in water, along with their experimental values.",
    "Here, we utilize a modified version of the dataset that includes the SMILES strings of the molecules and their corresponding experimental solvation free energy values.",
    "Dataset: The Delaney (ESOL) dataset is a regression dataset containing structures and water solubility data of 1128 compounds.",
    "This dataset is widely used to validate the ability of ML models to directly estimate solubility from molecular structures encoded as SMILES strings."
  ]
}